      },
      "description": "Shows the percentage of failed HTTP requests per endpoint. 4xx errors are client-side issues (e.g. 404 Not Found, 401 Unauthorized) meaning the request was invalid. 5xx errors are server-side issues (e.g. 500 Internal Server Error) meaning something went wrong in our application. A high 4xx rate may indicate invalid API calls from the simulator, while any 5xx errors should be investigated immediately.",
